/**
 * Creates a client-side interpreter that proxies all operations to a server.
 *
 * Each handler resolves its RuntimeEntry children via positional yield, then sends the resolved data to `{baseUrl}/mvfm/execute` as a JSON POST.
 *
 * @param options - Handler options.
 *
 * @param kinds - Kind strings to create handlers for (use Object.keys(plugin.kinds)).
 *
 * @returns An Interpreter that proxies all operations to the server.
 */
